A woman's body has been discovered buried under a bed in Vlakfontein, South of Johannesburg. It's suspected her boyfriend committed the murder. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A woman's body has been discovered buried under a bed in Vlakfontein, south of Johannesburg. It is suspected that her boyfriend committed the murder. READ: Vlakfontein community demands justice for murdered family Police are on scene to investigate the incident and a suspect has allegedly been arrested. Residents say justice must be served and he shouldn't receive bail because he is a danger to society. Vlakfontein is the same area where seven family members were found murdered and buried in a house last year.